stress on the first syllable not containing a, unless marked otherwise,

before consonants and finally, r = j. Short i, u, o are very open.
Short a = a A (oe). Long ii, u: tend to be diphthongal (ij, uw).
on = o+<n. Final a = Ot (n). e — e-r, a = a+.]
